---
title: Smoky Mustard Turkey Burgers with Seared Onion & Mixed Greens Salad
description: Juicy turkey burgers get an extra boost of flavor thanks to seared onion and smoky mustard, making this light and satisfying meal perfect for any night of the week. The flavorful patties are served on pillowy potato buns and paired with a crisp mixed green salad tossed with zesty Italian dressing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67619604bdfa7f79d1f16820-82daf377.jpeg
